The paper discusses deep learning and its application to various tasks such as speech recognition, image classification, and translation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions image captioning (cs.CV), attention mechanism (cs.CL), and sparsely-gated layers (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses joint training of multiple tasks (cs.SD).
